<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Reclamation Declined</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f4f6f8;
            font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
            color: #333333;
        }
        .email-wrapper {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 40px 0;
            background-color: #f4f6f8;
        }
        .email-content {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
        }
        .email-header {
            background-color: #fd7e14;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px 30px;
            font-size: 22px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .email-body {
            padding: 30px;
        }
        .email-body p {
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin: 15px 0;
        }
        .highlight {
            color: #fd7e14;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .email-footer {
            padding: 20px 30px;
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #777777;
            background-color: #f9fafb;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            margin-top: 20px;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background-color: #fd7e14;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 4px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        @media only screen and (max-width: 600px) {
            .email-body, .email-header, .email-footer {
                padding: 20px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="email-wrapper">
    <div class="email-content">
        <div class="email-header">
            ⚠️ Reclamation Declined
        </div>
        <div class="email-body">
            <p>Hello <strong>{{ user.prenom }} {{ user.nom }}</strong>,</p>

            <p>
                After a thorough review, we regret to inform you that your reclamation
                <strong>#{{ reclamation.reclamationId }}</strong> has been
                <span class="highlight">declined</span>.
            </p>

            <p>
                If you believe this was a mistake or have additional information, please don’t hesitate to reach out to our support team.
            </p>

            <a href="{{ support_url|default('#') }}" class="btn">Contact Support</a>

            <p>Thank you for your understanding,<br><strong>The Administration Team</strong></p>
        </div>
        <div class="email-footer">
            &copy; {{ "now"|date("Y") }} YourCompany. All rights reserved.<br>
            <small>This is an automated message — please do not reply.</small>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
